{"tid":2001330,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"手足想睇書，書本交流區。 麻煩各位手足幫幫手！！","createTime":"2020-05-04T12:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T14:12:14.000Z","uid":258097,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7289df4d9e5aecbe367f6ac0b5164ae674ad70df","tid":2001330,"uid":258097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"假如巴絲手足們都曾經成功入書俾在囚/還押人仕, 希望你們可以提供呢啲資訊造福其他想入書嘅手足<br />\n多謝你地既付出<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成功入到嘅<br />\n填書單<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/4i17GZUQSD6qDE2H9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4i17GZUQSD6qDE2H9&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=c8c92403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4i17GZUQSD6qDE2H9</a><br />\n睇書單<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zbpKy_wwH9Itaie4j6DoCFQC9vgJkqhzSe6lbnzpUKw/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1zbpKy_wwH9Itaie4j6DoCFQC9vgJkqhzSe6lbnzpUKw%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=47283554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zbpKy_wwH9Itaie4j6DoCFQC9vgJkqhzSe6lbnzpUKw/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n入唔到嘅<br />\n填禁書單<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/GUNgSASgfhFXKdPo8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FGUNgSASgfhFXKdPo8&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=d476067a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/GUNgSASgfhFXKdPo8</a><br />\n睇禁書單<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BYpN4btr1wqHbHn9pPwTbWbKy_0AUAy2ROUgfY2vMLM/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1BYpN4btr1wqHbHn9pPwTbWbKy_0AUAy2ROUgfY2vMLM%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=e909c2e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BYpN4btr1wqHbHn9pPwTbWbKy_0AUAy2ROUgfY2vMLM/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n書本要求<br />\n1. 雜誌、期刊及其他一般書刊(不包括教科書)<br />\n<br />\n- 每月上限6 本，包括宗教類書籍<br />\n- 儲存上限是 72 本，可以舊換新 ( 此上限有機會每處不同，留意 )<br />\n- 不可寫上任何字、塗鴉 ( 如簡單的祝福字句等都不可以 )<br />\n- 不可缺頁，不可是硬皮書、不可有夾層<br />\n- 不可帶敏感、任何淫褻及不雅資料(包括暴力、腐化)<br />\n- 如須帶更多宗教類書籍 / 參考書 / 其他書籍，須向福利官申請<br />\n- 可以參與宗教班，可向牧師索取《聖經》<br />\n<br />\n2. 宗教書籍<br />\n數量不限，但係聽講會先計咗落個6本度<br />\n<br />\n3. 教科書<br />\n教科書則可依照獲批准之數量收受<br />\n<br />\n法例<br />\n根據法例，所有來自外間的報章及書刊，若其内容或性質是不利於獄中任何在囚人士改過自新或對院所的保安、秩序及紀律造成威脅，署方可將其扣起，不予派發。所有隨報附送物品，必須通過保安檢查及符合指定規格，並獲管方批准，方可派發予在囚人士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關文章<br />\n【抗暴之戰】懲教署打壓在囚抗爭者 禁收《蘋果》逆權月曆<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200115/UIYVEVDM3FN5FIJUTOOA3STISE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200115%2FUIYVEVDM3FN5FIJUTOOA3STISE%2F&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=34266af9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200115%2FUIYVEVDM3FN5FIJUTOOA3STISE%2F&h=ece6c6d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200115/UIYVEVDM3FN5FIJUTOOA3STISE/</a><br />\n<br />\n監房睇書有限制？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1036883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1036883&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=9a56f4a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1036883&h=c71f74a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1036883</a><br />\n<br />\n東北告急，無你點得 ? 問題二：可唔以入野比佢呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lovenent/photos/a.481177521992206/1315248365251780/?type=1&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flovenent%2Fphotos%2Fa.481177521992206%2F1315248365251780%2F%3Ftype%3D1%26theater&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=c5f56bb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lovenent/photos/a.481177521992206/1315248365251780/?type=1&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n探訪在還押或在囚人士<br />\n<a href=\"http://youknowlaw.caritas.org.hk/%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%AA%E5%9C%A8%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E6%88%96%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyouknowlaw.caritas.org.hk%2F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%259B%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%2F&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=3ff42808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://youknowlaw.caritas.org.hk/%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%AA%E5%9C%A8%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E6%88%96%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB/</a>"},{"pid":"10c945a3d992ad16ce6fd1ebfb8a888eb8c7cc48","tid":2001330,"uid":346476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5baa089ae450c814fa47ad3ef99c34f99c1a7ce","tid":2001330,"uid":258097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"真係好想收集到大家入到同入唔到書嘅資料<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拜托啦 咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家普遍嚟講 政治書都入唔到<br />\n通常佢哋覺得會擾亂秩序嘅書都唔會入到"},{"pid":"653b0a4036c8ef990806e72d5b2813cee55bb97c","tid":2001330,"uid":75583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fabd4755b423868ce5435b7d4ba5fa167c85e14b","tid":2001330,"uid":258097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"想買書可以支持翻本土書店啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒埋入去睇香港邊度有本土書店啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屬於香港人嘅書店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2000687</a><br />\n- 